    dc:description "FIGURES 29–36. Sessiluncus aegypticus Nasr &Affifi.29. Male, gnathotectum; 30. Male, chelicera; 31. Female, subcapitulum (inset); 32. Female, dorsal (inner) view of hypostom; 33. Female, palp; 34. Female, chelicera; 35. Female, trochanter IV; 36. Female, femur III. Abbreviations: lb, labrum; plb, paralabrum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5649493/files/figure.png" ;
